{"id": 1715, "genre": 1001, "title": "你什么时候因为嫌麻烦放弃了消费功课？", "description": "买化妆品会看二十篇测评，花三十分钟学习“皂基”“水杨酸”的基础知识，但关于如何买一根信号超稳定的数据线，我主要靠“瞎猫碰上死耗子”。（题图来自：giphy）", "record_count": 2206, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170601121143y2vJtPdTWFbl6XRD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-03T17:00:16Z", "options": [{"id": 209408, "content": "花时间买节省的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046921}, {"id": 209409, "content": "学生党大干皮想买个500以内的粉底液，看了俩月还没下手，主要穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781199}, {"id": 209410, "content": "枕头的填充物有，鸭绒，苦荞，记忆棉，丝棉，谷壳………天啊，我到底适合哪种？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790723}, {"id": 209412, "content": "消费欲望高涨到控制不住自己的时侯 \n话说前段时间为了买手机  硬是忍受了一星期没手机的日子 看了一周的各种测评 。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031351}, {"id": 209413, "content": "买电脑，研究对比了快一个月，最后在我妈给我的预算范围内买了个最贵的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118439}, {"id": 209415, "content": "小米618 好货不用挑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039638}, {"id": 209417, "content": "就是懒\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838530}, {"id": 209418, "content": "比着比着，越比越贵，干脆不买了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019577}, {"id": 209419, "content": "买条裙子看了一个月 看着看着钱花完了 索性不买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047203}, {"id": 209420, "content": "眼花缭乱的攻略，太累了，买自己用过的值得信赖的品牌就好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882709}, {"id": 209422, "content": "海洋之谜只有一个缺点就是贵…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905507}, {"id": 209423, "content": "买护肤品，看完成分党的分析，觉得用什么对皮肤都是负担的时候?", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046075}, {"id": 209681, "content": "配置好的永远是最贵的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047936}, {"id": 210195, "content": "买beats耳机，一个头戴一个入耳，然而和我的苹果耳机比起来听不出什么差别", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049152}, {"id": 209429, "content": "所以买苹果手机，因为省事儿不用挑；安卓好，可是懒得去了解那么多牌子和型号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046942}, {"id": 209432, "content": "因为穷啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047259}, {"id": 209433, "content": "当谷歌不能用，百度搜不到的时候，我就放弃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047265}, {"id": 209436, "content": "当然是在发工资的当日了！管它什么成份价格，爷有钱。买完就是孙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191760}, {"id": 209438, "content": "自从用上Mac和iPhone，从此再不关心什么参数配置。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 209442, "content": "装修的时候，因为短期要买好许多东西，不太贵的就没做功课。平时有做功课，知道自己在干什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123188}, {"id": 211234, "content": "在某宝逛到想吐，然而还是没找到自己喜欢的，最后乱七八糟的选了一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050961}, {"id": 209444, "content": "组装电脑为了便宜 点开了一个叫图拉丁的贴吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898427}, {"id": 209446, "content": "买品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875347}, {"id": 210224, "content": "香水味道好多，一个一个试太麻烦，干脆不买了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207346}, {"id": 209457, "content": "货比三家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964341}, {"id": 209458, "content": "几个原则:1、消费能力范围内\n2、物品没有等级之分", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794066}, {"id": 209461, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20170604175836kYAtcnflxidyNV16.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015459}, {"id": 209464, "content": "看了无数口红的试用评价 最后买了国货雅邦9.9?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032404}, {"id": 209467, "content": "大商场就一定是正货。货比三家都懒得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714089}, {"id": 210493, "content": "还是穷，有钱的话就直接买最贵的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817658}, {"id": 209470, "content": "直接某东销量第一的买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742392}, {"id": 209471, "content": "需要尺子量而身边没有尺子的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679825}, {"id": 209472, "content": "太麻烦，所以现在都是一眼定生死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984475}, {"id": 209473, "content": "下班回来累得要死又不得不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 209475, "content": "以前觉得便宜的东西不会太好  用过贵的以后 我越发确信  便宜确实没好货", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979250}, {"id": 209476, "content": "做完功课发现买的还是不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046874}, {"id": 209477, "content": "贵≠好 但一定=不那么差", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940928}, {"id": 209478, "content": "男生还会对除了电子产品其他的更下功夫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875588}, {"id": 209480, "content": "有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043905}, {"id": 209483, "content": "问熟人不就行了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701087}, {"id": 209739, "content": "专柜试用，电商比价，海淘下单。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642016}, {"id": 209484, "content": "还是要买品牌贵货，用着放心也不舍得扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869056}, {"id": 209486, "content": "追求性价比高的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92975}, {"id": 209488, "content": "不紧要的东西，凑合就行，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047362}, {"id": 209493, "content": "想比对尿不湿好坏，发现都是微商们各说各的好，决定每种买一包，以宝宝的屁股来决定…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495011}, {"id": 209494, "content": "你说什么？财团B?!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019759}, {"id": 209496, "content": "线下消费时。会很困难地抑制住不上网查一下的欲望接受所见即所得的线下购物本身带来的一丝不同于网购的快乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047404}, {"id": 209497, "content": "请私教。不用看任何健身文章，营养文章，健身餐等等资料。一个好的私教一网打尽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991656}, {"id": 209501, "content": "之前亚马逊活动满200海外购包邮，半个月内海外购两次，都是囤货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012140}, {"id": 209502, "content": "大概是觉得某些东西的某些属性好坏并不影响生活愉悦度???关键是因为感知不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047439}]}